verbose_text: Consistent with the unperturbed proliferation and differentiation properties of AAV-Cre-transduced tdTomato + satellite cells, relative quantification of myogenic gene expression indicated equivalent levels of Pax7, Myf5, and Myog expression, with a slight (~ 25%) reduction in Myod1 in tdTomato + satellite cells compared to tdTomato - satellite cells (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
